.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.BR gcvt ()
function converts \fInumber\fP ta a minimal length null-terminated
ASCII strang n' stores tha result up in \fIbuf\fP.
It produces \fIndigit\fP dope digits up in either
.BR printf (3)
F format or E format.
.SH RETURN VALUE
The
.BR gcvt ()
function returns tha address of tha strang pointed to
by \fIbuf\fP.
